      "Calculation": "For calculation of interest, the period would be taken as six months, which is the average period assuming that the amount is withdrawn evenly in the middle of the month throughout the year.",
      "Interest Calculation": "The amount of interest on drawings works out to be Rs. 2,400 as follows:",
      "Formula": "Rs. 60,000 x 8 / 100 x 12 = Rs. 2,400"
    }
  },
  "Guarantee of Profit to a Partner": "1.6"
